  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zaru is a single-player, first-person, retro-style horror game in which your goal is to lock up a warehouse on a night whilst avoiding various monsters that can only be detected by giving up sight, hearing or speech through in-game mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Synopsis</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a warehouse worker in 1980's America. Your job is to lock up the warehouse on an evening after work. Except you aren't alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beings roam behind and between the shelves. Beings that can't be perceived conventionally. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To witness their movements you will have to give up one sense to enhance another e.g. giving up your sight to be able to accurately hear a being and where it is. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between your senses to keep on top of the beings' movements while making sure you don't neglect any of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive, you must complete various tasks given by fellow employees, lock up and don't let the beings touch you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No-one is around to save you when something goes wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoiding the monsters by swapping your sensory prowess</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doing tasks left by fellow workers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shouting at a pigeon to get it out of the warehouse</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Microphone required for gameplay, headphones recommended for intended experience.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zaru is a single-player, first-person, retro-style horror game in which your goal is to lock up a warehouse on a night whilst avoiding various monsters that can only be detected by giving up sight, hearing or speech through in-game mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Synopsis</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a warehouse worker in 1980's America. Your job is to lock up the warehouse on an evening after work. Except you aren't alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beings roam behind and between the shelves. Beings that can't be perceived conventionally. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To witness their movements you will have to give up one sense to enhance another e.g. giving up your sight to be able to accurately hear a being and where it is. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between your senses to keep on top of the beings' movements while making sure you don't neglect any of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive, you must complete various tasks given by fellow employees, lock up and don't let the beings touch you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No-one is around to save you when something goes wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoiding the monsters by swapping your sensory prowess</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/63879dd26ad61c50fb1fbdc729ab49d2.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doing tasks left by fellow workers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/142b21facdd9e1bac5a636e49dc24f22.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shouting at a pigeon to get it out of the warehouse</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.poster.avif?t=1729692257\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.webm?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071750/extras/d90210b56cf81cba8ae1e2da5a782152.mp4?t=1729692257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Microphone required for gameplay, headphones recommended for intended experience.</p>",
